name: Black Market
description: Add cards from outside the supply pile.

name: Stash
description: When you shuffle, you may put this anywhere in your deck.

name: Envoy
description: Reveal the top 5 cards of your deck. The player to your left chooses 1 for you to discard. Draw the rest.

name: Walled Village
description: You can re-play this card in set circumstances.

name: Prince
description: Choose an Action card costing 4 or less. You play that card for free every turn. Set Prince aside.

name: Bonfire
description: Trash up to 2 cards in play.
